title: War of the Roses: Scratches On the Fender of Their Car
description: Rachel is wondering if there's something go on with her fiance, Drew, and his co-worker because the co-worker seems super flirty with him AND she found weird scratches on the front of their car that she thinks might be from women's jeans.  Is Rachel over-analyzing things or is her fiance a little too close with his co-worker?
